text: Rinze-chan, this gratin looks delicious too!

Hey, everyone.
Are you all reading magazines?

Yes. It's a feature called
"Happiness Recipes to Capture His Heart".

...Um, Producer-sama, would you...
be willing to cook for me...? I mean, do you cook...?

I-I understand...
I'll do my best...

I see! Is it hard to knead
if you want to make it by hand properly...?

Oh, that's convenient, isn't it?
It'll be good training for you.

Gyoza!
Making them is fun and eating them is delicious, right?
Oh, how about having a gyoza party with everyone next time?!
